# Embeddable Chatbot Builder

Build a landing page and clickable web app prototype for a chatbot builder. Users upload company documents and knowledge to create a chatbot. The chatbot is available inside the app as a ChatGPT-style chat interface and as an embeddable widget for customer websites.

Treat this as a launch-ready product concept, not a throwaway demo. No backend is required — a clickable prototype with strong design and product feel is sufficient.

## Requirements

- Landing page that communicates product value and drives onboarding
- Chat interface for document upload and in-app bot testing
- Embeddable widget builder with copy/paste embed code
- Paywall with pricing plans and logically gated features
- Additional pages and features as defined in [product.mdc](./product.mdc)

## Deliverables

- Landing page
- Web app for building chatbots
- Presentation: video demo (preferred) or written tutorial with screenshots

## Criteria

- **Design quality:** Distinct brand and personality; not generic AI template aesthetics. Use Mobbin, Dribbble, or comparable references for proven patterns.
- **Product thinking:** Clear onboarding, intentional user flow, no extraneous features. Follow the sequence defined in product.mdc: onboarding → aha (test chat) → embed → paywall.
- **Attention to detail:** Animations, micro-interactions, copywriting, and overall polish.

## Acceptance Checklist

- Landing page communicates value and drives sign-up
- Builder flow: upload docs → test chat → widget preview → copy embed code
- Free tier limits are visible: 1 bot, 5 documents, watermark on widget
- Paywall triggers contextually on Pro/Business gates (branding, analytics, second bot, API)
- Chat UI includes suggested questions, typing indicator, and source citations (mocked)
